Command Overview
================

Archiving and Compressing
-------------------------

To archive and compress files f1.txt, f2.txt, and f3.txt using tar and gzip

	tar -czvf compressed_arcive_name.tar.gz *.txt
	
	or

	tar -czvf compressed_archive_name.tar.gz f1.txt f2.txt f3.txt

To archive and compress files f1.txt, f2.txt, and f3.txt using tar and bzip2 
	
	tar -cjvf compressed_arcive_name.tar.bz2 *.txt
	
	or

	tar -cjvf compressed_archive_name.tar.bz2 f1.txt f2.txt f3.txt

Extracting and Decompressing
----------------------------
 
To extract and decompress files f1.txt, f2.txt, and f3.txt using tar and gzip

	tar -xzvf compressed_arcive_name.tar.gz
	

